data.description: True MULTIGENERATIONAL home sitting pretty on a 0.72 ACRE LOT that backs up to a conservation area in quaint community of Lake Helen. 2 homes in one. 5 Bedrooms, 4 Baths contemporary Masterpiece. OVER 3,400 Sq Ft. home with an amazing Floor plan offering 2 Living rooms, 2 dining rooms, one for each side of the home. As you step into the entryway there is a spacious Living room and formal dining room with beautiful hardwood floors. The Kitchen is every cooks dream and the heart of the home. Kitchen and dining area is done in Travertine tile. There are 3 bedrooms and two full baths on this side of the home. You can step out from the kitchen to a Vinyl Fenced courtyard, perfect for your fur babies or playground area. As you walk through the kitchen into the 2nd area, it is perfect for In-laws to have their own space or Great room for entertaining from the Lanai and pool area. Great room has a wood burning fireplace to cozy up on the couch during the cooler months. Offers 2 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, dining room space or exercise room. You can step through to the  18 x 19 covered lanai area and relax and enjoy the brand new salt water pool and spa. You will be able to enjoy this year round since it is solar heated. . Home has two interior Laundry/Utility Rooms. With an oversized 23 x 33 Side-Entry garage with workshop area or storage area. Garage has pull down access to a large floored storage area. Exterior storage shed conveys. Minutes to I-4 easy access. 30 min drive to the Beaches and 40 min drive to Orlando. Brand new roof and solar was installed this year and has two Tesla Battery backup units that will run the entire home, except pool in any power outage. 2 Hot water heaters for each side of the home. Panel Box was updated when new solar system was installed.
